{"tid":56043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普砲轟聯合國 淪為「聊天玩樂俱樂部」","createTime":"2016-12-27T01:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T11:00:38.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb77752100bebdba0e0bdf7dc8deeca103586a0e","tid":56043,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:24:39.000Z","msg":"川普砲轟聯合國 淪為「聊天玩樂俱樂部」<br />\n<br />\n2016/12/27 08:52&nbsp;1089<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會上周以14:0通過決議，譴責以色列在巴勒斯坦地區持續屯墾。美國候任總統川普（Donald Trump）周一在推特發文，質疑決議的效果，稱聯合國「只是一個讓大家聚在一起玩樂的俱樂部」。川普說，聯合國「有龐大潛力」，卻淪為「讓大家聚在一起聊天玩樂的俱樂部」，「真悲哀！」<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThe United Nations has such great potential but right now it is just a club for people to get together, talk and have a good time. So sad!<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump)&nbsp;2016年12月26日<br />\n<br />\n川普上周五曾警告，他下月20日就職後，聯合國「會不一樣」。聯合國就譴責以色列的決議進行表決前，川普曾發推文，要求美國如往例行使否決權，但與以色列關係冰冷的歐巴馬政府堅持棄權。 （國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161227/1021485/川普砲轟聯合國　淪為「聊天玩樂俱樂部」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161227%2F1021485%2F%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A0%B2%E8%BD%9F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%80%E6%B7%AA%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%A9%E6%A8%82%E4%BF%B1%E6%A8%82%E9%83%A8%E3%80%8D&d=rwA%2B5pHQ3r474X4t2NstPGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=dff28172\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161227/1021485/川普砲轟聯合國　淪為「聊天玩樂俱樂部」</a>"},{"pid":"4d8bbfc7360a343d42b9001e70c803fd24a6d5cb","tid":56043,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039beb9d72feaa4e56e4e17c9665619d15aa3645","tid":56043,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"So sad!"},{"pid":"7a1c2b322855a96d2c19d889f4460288082